
=== Building the honeypot ===

You have to build the two device drivers "GhostBus.sys" and "GhostDrive.sys"
as well as the command line tool "GhostTool.exe" from the source code.
Please see http://code.google.com/p/ghost-usb-honeypot/wiki/BuildGuide for
instructions.


=== Installing the honeypot ===

Once you have compiled the code, you can install Ghost on your system.
For detailed instructions on how to do so, please refer to
http://code.google.com/p/ghost-usb-honeypot/wiki/InstallGuide.